title: Escape From The Planet Of The Apes 1971 with greek subs.avi
description:
Escape From The Planet Of The Apes 1971 with greek subs

apodrash apo ton planhth ton pithikon 1971 me ellhnikoys ypotitloys


Thelontas na mathoyn ti syneveh sto parelthon kai oi pithikoi apekthsan anthropines ikanothtes,o kornilios,h zira kai enas akoma syntrofos toys taksideyoyn piso sto xrono. Vriskontai sto los antzeles toy 20oy aiona,opoy oi anthropoid toys ypodexontai arxika me enthoysiasmo.omos syntoma oi pithikoi episthmones vriskontai kynhghmenoi.
